        <p><strong>The speaker is the person who is talking or writing.</strong></p>

        <h3>Examples</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>A rapper performing a verse on stage</li>
          <li>A teacher giving directions in class</li>
          <li>A person giving a speech at a protest or meeting</li>
        </ul>

        <p class="note">On your worksheet, question 1 should say: “The <strong>speaker</strong> is the person who is talking or writing.”</p>
