            <li><strong>Where</strong> – Where did she live and travel in the video?</li>
            <li><strong>What</strong> – What important things did she do in her life?</li>
            <li><strong>Why</strong> – Why did she keep traveling and speaking?</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

